            <title>[DERBY-5986] Make ArithmeticTest test DECIMAL data type</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5986</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed in the code coverage report that the DECIMAL data type has less test coverage than the other numeric data types. One way to improve it may be to make existing tests for other numeric types also test the DECIMAL type. ArithmeticTest is one such test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
